{"tid":1605510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"片段顯示警棍多次打被捕學生腳　中大講師拍攝被警指駡","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:09:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e77cd3200f85d48be3ae229bb0caaabb4247a7","tid":1605510,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"警方昨日下午在金鐘制服多人，<span style=\"color: red;\">有片段顯示，有被捕人士被制服期間，頭部流血，有速龍小隊懷疑用腳繼續踏著對方身體</span>。<br />\n<br />\n根據<span style=\"color: red;\">中大新聞與傳播學院講師譚蕙芸</span>昨日在金鐘太古廣場外拍攝的片段，一名被制服、佩戴防毒口罩的男子身體被警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以腳踏著，男子頭部正流血，地上有一灘鮮血，譚蕙芸當時多次向警方指出，他的頭部流血，但不獲理會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n一名同樣被制服男子向鏡頭5次叫喊個人名字以及所屬學校名稱，期間曾被人以手遮蓋口部。當時警員要求譚蕙芸離開，並指罵對方「行開啦、八婆」。警方之後以盾牌遮檔男子臉部，以警棍多次向該男子揮動，根據譚蕙芸在社交網站描述，<span style=\"color: red;\">警員以警棍打了被捕學生的腳至少6次</span>。片段所見，在場警員多次阻礙拍攝，以盾牌阻擋鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n趙聿修紀念中學證實這是該校一名中六學生，家人已知悉事件，直至今晨5時，學生仍然留院。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483407-20190930.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483407-20190930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=d9cae55c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483407-20190930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=07b20051\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483407-20190930.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"744dd202310329e4d613988cb2e0243b22ee1727","tid":1605510,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wwviviantam/videos/2533822440030504/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwwviviantam%2Fvideos%2F2533822440030504%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=7ec1b336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wwviviantam/videos/2533822440030504/</a>"}]}